survey.music_making: In high school, I took voice lessons for one term and I was in the chorus for one year (maybe half a year). I participated in one concert performance. Otherwise, I listen to music non-stop most days and I enjoy live musical performances.
survey.habit_change: I listen to less new stuff than I have in the past. As a youth, I'd say 75% of the music I listened to was new to me. Now, I'd say that number is more like 10-15% of my music is new to me.
survey.habits: I really listen to music when I am awake. It doesn't matter if I'm cooking, reading, working, I am listening to music unless I am actively watching visual media. Sometimes, I'm listening to music then too.
